                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-defend2093" type="age" value="13"></interp>
                  </persName>
             &amp; 
               
                  <persName id="t18310908-289-defend2095" type="defendantName">
                     MARY 
                     DONOUGH
                  <interp inst="t18310908-289-defend2095" type="surname" value="DONOUGH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-defend2095" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-defend2095" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-defend2095" type="age" value="15"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             were indicted for <rs id="t18310908-289-off1483" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-off1483" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-off1483" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18310908-289-cd1484" type="crimeDate">31st of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-289-off1483 t18310908-289-cd1484"></join>, 1 coat, value 14s.; 1 pair of trousers, value 10s.; 1 shawl, value 16s., and 1 handkerchief, value 1s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18310908-289-victim2097" type="victimName">
                     Michael 
                     Ryan
                  <interp inst="t18310908-289-victim2097" type="surname" value="Ryan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-victim2097" type="given" value="Michael"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-victim2097" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-289-off1483 t18310908-289-victim2097"></join>
                  </persName>
               
            .</p>
               <p>MARY RYAN. I am the wife of 
               <persName id="t18310908-289-person2098">
                  Michael 
                  Ryan
               <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2098" type="surname" value="Ryan"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2098" type="given" value="Michael"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2098" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             - we live in <placeName id="t18310908-289-crimeloc1485">Drury-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-289-crimeloc1485" type="placeName" value="Drury-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-289-crimeloc1485" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-289-off1483 t18310908-289-crimeloc1485"></join>; Boniface was employed to nurse my child - I know nothing of Donough. On Sunday, the 31st of July, my husband went to clean himself, and missed these articles; I had seen them all safe on the Friday night, in the trunk, which stood between two beds; my husband kept the key in his pocket - I had Donough taken, in consequence of what Boniface said.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-289-person2099">
                  WILLIAM 
                  OLIVER
               <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2099" type="surname" value="OLIVER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2099" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2099" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lodge in a small room adjoining the prosecutor's. On Saturday, the 30th of July, I saw Boniface in their room, alone, but soon afterwards the other prisoner joined her; I then went out - Donough had been<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183109080129"></xptr>there in the morning, to know if Mr. Ryan would want Boniface that day, and I said yes; I left them in the room - I returned in half an hour, and they were gone.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-289-person2100">
                  SAMUEL 
                  FLETCHER
               <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2100" type="surname" value="FLETCHER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2100" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2100" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to a pawnbroker. On the 30th of July Boniface came to our shop, and pawned the coat and trousers; a person, who I believe was Donough, was with her.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-289-person2101">
                  JOSEPH 
                  HEWITSON
               <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2101" type="surname" value="HEWITSON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2101" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2101" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to a pawnbroker, in Gray's Inn-lane. On the 30th of July, in the morning, between eleven and twelve o'clock, Donough came to our shop with another girl, and pawned this handkerchief and shoes.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-289-person2102">
                  WILLIAM 
                  ROBINSON
               <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2102" type="surname" value="ROBINSON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2102" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-person2102" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. I took the prisoners together, on the 31st of July, in St. Giles'.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>BONIFACE - <rs id="t18310908-289-verdict1486" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18310908-289-verdict1486" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 13.</p>
               <p>DONOUGH - <rs id="t18310908-289-verdict1487" type="verdictDescription">
